WEBVTT

00:06:25.880 --> 00:06:30.720
or the first time your new computer
manager issues an order at work.

00:06:33.800 --> 00:06:36.920
But when I sat at that first game,

00:06:38.080 --> 00:06:40.216
I couldn't be sure

00:06:40.240 --> 00:06:43.920
what is this thing capable of.

00:06:44.920 --> 00:06:48.080
Technology can advance in leaps,
and IBM had invested heavily.

00:06:48.680 --> 00:06:49.880
I lost that game.

00:06:52.320 --> 00:06:54.096
And I couldn't help wondering,

00:06:54.120 --> 00:06:55.680
might it be invincible?

00:06:56.600 --> 00:06:58.960
Was my beloved game of chess over?